snippet.title: IT STARES BACK PROLOGUE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Explore The Great Tapestry: Once a candy-colored realm of dreams and fantasy, now a corrupted death-scape of perilous ruin. Will you gaze into the void to learn the fate of this tattered land? Be weary, traveler…

Choose your faction and play the Prologue:
https://discord.gg/3Jfc7C2

There may yet be another way to unlock the prologue's hidden mysteries, but such knowledge will surely lead to madness.

enter-the-void
